org.egov.commons

Class Installment

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.egov.commons.Installment
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<Installment>

    public class Installment
extends Object
implements Serializable, Comparable<Installment>
    This class represents an Installment. Every installment has an year, it should start from the current financial year, and it is assumed that it spans untill the end of the current financial year,which falls in the next year. There can be one or more installments in a year, each representing a particular period in that year.
